          A list of ObjectBuilders defining the new annotations created by UIMA that should be mapped back into GATE.

        • outputsUpdated

          List<E> outputsUpdated
          A list of ObjectBuilders defining the annotations whose features have been updated by UIMA, and for which changes should be propagated back into GATE.

        • outputsRemoved
